David Pinner https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Pinner 0 Pinner is a town in the London Borough of Harrow in northwest London, England, 12 miles (19 km) from Charing Cross. It is also in the historic county of Middlesex. Pinner is a_town in the_London_Borough of Harrow in northwest_London_,_England , 12_miles ( 19_km ) from Charing_Cross . It is also in the_historic_county of Middlesex .
